## Design Considerations

The application uses Material Design 3 with a deep navy base (#0D1B2A) and emerald green
accent (#1BCC8A). All touch targets meet the 48dp Android accessibility minimum. Input
validation is applied throughout. The architecture separates data, business logic, and
presentation into clearly defined layers. The dashboard is organised into three sections:
Core Features, Analytics, and Own Features.

