## GitHub Actions

Automated CI/CD is configured in .github/workflows/build.yml.
On every push to main the workflow:
1. Sets up JDK 17
2. Runs all unit tests via ./gradlew test
3. Builds the debug APK via ./gradlew assembleDebug
4. Uploads the APK as a downloadable artifact

Reference: https://github.com/IMAD5112/Github-actions/blob/main/.github/workflows/build.yml

