## Tech Stack

- Language: Kotlin
- IDE: Android Studio
- Database: Room DB (SQLite)
- Graph library: MPAndroidChart v3.1.0
- UI: Material Design 3, RecyclerView, ViewBinding
- Photo: Camera Intent with FileProvider
- Security: SHA-256 password hashing
- CI/CD: GitHub Actions

